main event: Unidentified personnel of the Operations Section at Marshall AFB, Kansas, reported sighting a beam-shaped object over the base on 25 May 1953.
interesting points: The sighting lasted from 10:15 AM to 11:15 AM, The reported object was described as beam-shaped, Observers estimated the object's speed at approximately 322 mph and altitude at around 330 feet, The sighting prompted communication and analysis at various military levels, This incident was documented under Project Blue Book for further investigation.
witness description: unidentified personnel of the Operations Section
